                    </div>
                    <div class="col-xs-12 col-lg-4">
                        <h2><i class="img-icon img-icon-person"></i>service & installation</h2>
                        <p>After finding and selecting a car part for your needs you are welcome to use our car part replacement services, performed by our quilified personel at our own car service.</p>
